import React from 'react'
import NextHead from 'next/head'

const Head = ({ }) => (
  <NextHead>
    <meta charSet="UTF-8" />
    <title>PetroGas oil & Construction Ltd</title>
    <meta name="description" content= 'PetroGas oil & Construction Ltd is a leading company which deals with wide range of products, including petroleum, oil, gas and construction engineering' />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="icon" href="favicon.jpg" sizes="16x16" type="image/png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Zilla+Slab:400,700" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css"></link>
  </NextHead>
)

export default Head
